cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.DC 

This paper deals with interference mitigation techniques in wireless cellular networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization and control algorithms, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper uses simulations to evaluate the algorithms, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
